                      "name": "If iCloud Backup or iCloud Drive is enabled on your device, iOS may automatically store a copy of the App’s data in your personal iCloud account. This process is entirely managed by Apple, and we do not have access to or control over that data. For more details, please refer to the Apple Privacy Policy.",
